      "date": "2011-03-28 13:25:19.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nSanity test 155{a,b,c,d} passed on master branch:\n\n- the minimum available size of OST > the large file size:\\\\\nhttps://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/496b5408-593b-11e0-a272-52540025f9af\n\n- the minimum available size of OST < the large file size:\\\\\nhttps://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/27a554c6-593c-11e0-a272-52540025f9af",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
    {
